import React from "react"
import {Nav,NavIcons,NavItems,NavItem,NavRight,AvatarImg,Search,Fb,Insta,Pin,Twit,Info} from "./styles/navstyle"
const Navbar = () =>{
    return(
        <Nav>
            <NavIcons>
                <Fb  />
                <Insta />
                <Pin />
                <Twit />
            </NavIcons>
            <NavItems>
                <NavItem to = "/">HOME</NavItem>
                <NavItem>ABOUT</NavItem>
                <NavItem>CONTACT</NavItem>
                <NavItem>WRITE</NavItem>
                <NavItem to = "/login">LOGIN</NavItem>
            </NavItems>
            <NavRight>
                <AvatarImg src = "https://media.vogue.co.uk/photos/60412c1641a91443172b7a4e/2:3/w_1280,h_1920,c_limit/April21%20Hollywood%20Portfolio%20Tom%20Holland.jpg" />
                <Search />
                <Info />
            </NavRight>
        </Nav>
    )
}
export default Navbar
